Here is a rough development plan for each version

ver 0.9
- add line or pie chart for statistics
- add more useful charts
- use crontab to generate default charts for performance boost
- add navigation interface to charts so that users can jump easier
- divide text messages for better i18n

ver 1.x
- show changeset for each file 
(add source navigation interface which supports changeset history)
- add theme ability so that users can choose site design

ver 2.x
- support multiple git tree
